{% comment %}
Auto-link glossary terms in content.
Usage: {% render 'auto-link-glossary', content: article.content %}
{% endcomment %}

{% assign terms = pages['jewelry-glossary'].metafields.custom.glossary_terms.value %}
{% assign new_content = content | default: '' %}

{%- capture real_kemp_old_weight_text -%}Real kemp pieces are also noticeably heavier than regular alloy-metal dance jewellery because of the brass and copper base. For young dancers or long performance days, that weight is worth considering along with the stage look.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- capture real_kemp_new_weight_text -%}In Anil Tunk's hands-on experience, real kemp pieces of similar size often feel noticeably heavier and more substantial than regular alloy-metal dance jewellery because of the brass and copper base. For young dancers or long performance days, that weight is worth considering along with the stage look.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- assign new_content = new_content | replace: real_kemp_old_weight_text, real_kemp_new_weight_text -%}

{% if terms and terms.size > 0 %}
  {% for term in terms %}
    {% assign link = '<a href="/pages/jewelry-glossary" class="gc-glossary-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">' | append: term.name | append: '</a>' %}
    {%- assign new_content = new_content | replace_first: term.name, link -%}
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{{ new_content }}
